H0.text: What is a more common name for the umbilicus. Belly Button

H3.text: What is a more common name for the umbilicus. Navel

A4.text: also known as the belly button

A5.text: The navel (clinically known as the umbilicus; also known as the belly button or tummy button)

A6.text: The navel is a protruding, flat, or hollowed area on the abdomen at the attachment site of the umbilical cord.
